-1 MOTD~
. `YNew features `w(you can view this list any time with '`Gmotd`w')
    1. Mudweiser has returned! Kyle Boyd provided me with the source
       code, and areas, races, classes, skills, and other bits of
       Mudweiser have been incorporated here.
    2. The stock EmberMUD areas are still accessible. There are two
       Midgaards. By default you start in Mudweiser's Midgaard. You
       can travel between the two via a portal in the Temple Square.
       All rooms in the stock Midgaard are colored `Ggreen`w.
    3. You can now choose where you recall. Type '`Gbeacon`w' to set your
       recall point to the current room. If you get stuck, you can reset
       your beacon to the Temple of Mota with '`Gbeaconreset`w'.
    4. The Mudpi bot has been removed. However, healing rates are
       greatly increased while sleeping on the temple altar.
~
