-1 GATE~
. `GCAST GATE <name>                                                      `Yspell
`K- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
 `wThe gate spell is a powerful transportation magic that opens up a   
 portal between your character and another person or creature        
 somewhere else in the world. This portal will transport you and    
 any pet you might have, but not other members of your group.        
                                                                     
 Monsters recieve a save against gate, and monsters or players more  
 than 3 levels higher than you can not be gated to at all. God       
 and private rooms cannot be gated to, and no recall rooms cannot be 
 gated out of. Finally, all gods are immune to gate.                                                                  
~
-1 FLEE~
. `GFLEE                                                           `Ycombat skill
`K- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
 `wOnce you start a fight, you can't just walk away from it. If the   
 fight is not going well, you can attempt to FLEE (You can also      
 RECALL, but this is less likely to work, and costs more experience  
 points than fleeing).                                               
                                                                     
 If you lose your connection during a fight, then your character will
 keep fighting, and will attempt to RECALL from time to time. Your       
 chances of making the recall are reduced, and you will lose much    
 more experience.                                                    
                                                                     
 `WSee also: `GRECALL WIMPY                                             
~
