 strength by one.
~
0 'CONTINUAL LIGHT'~
. `GCAST 'CONTINUAL LIGHT'                                                `Yspell
`K- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
 `wThis spell creates a ball of light, which you can hold as a light source.
 The ball of light will last indefinitely.
~
0 'CONTROL WEATHER'~
