`K- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
 `wThis spell replenishes a drink container with water.
~
0 'CURE BLINDNESS'~
. `GCAST 'CURE BLINDNESS' <character>                                     `Yspell
`K- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
 `wThis spell cures blindness in one so unfortunate.
~
0 'CURE POISON'~
. `GCAST 'CURE POISON' <character>                                        `Yspell
`K- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
 `wThis spell cures poison in one so unfortunate.
~
0 'CURE LIGHT' 'CURE SERIOUS' 'CURE CRITICAL' HEAL RESTORATION~
. `GCAST 'CURE LIGHT' <character>
 CAST 'CURE SERIOUS' <character>
 CAST 'CURE CRITICAL' <character>
 CAST 'HEAL' <character>
 CAST 'RESTORATION' <character>                                        `Yspell
