 heal more damage.

 (see 'help healer' for details on the heal command)
~
0 CURSE~
. `GCAST 'CURSE' <character>                                              `Yspell
`K- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
 `wThis spell reduces the character's to-hit roll and save versus spells.
