 `wThis spell enables the caster to detect evil characters, which will
 reveal a characteristic red aura.
~
0 'DETECT HIDDEN'~
. `GCAST 'DETECT HIDDEN'                                                  `Yspell
`K- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
 `wThis spell enables the caster to detect hidden creatures.
~
0 'DETECT INVIS'~
. `GCAST 'DETECT INVIS'                                                   `Yspell
`K- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
 `wThis spell enables the caster to detect invisible objects and characters.
~
