 is created.  It can also be used to reduce the amount of exp required
 per level.

 GAIN LIST lists all the skills and spell groups you can gain, and their
 costs in training sessions.

 GAIN POINTS lowers your creation points by one, and costs two training 
 sessions.

 GAIN CONVERT converts seven practices to one training session.

 GAIN REVERT converts one training session to five practice sessions.

 GAIN <skill> gives you that skill or spell group.
